data.description: This beautiful 4 bedrooms/3 baths home has so much to offer! All the space and upgrades you need! Very open floor plan. Eat-in Kitchen with stained custom cabinetry and lighting, granite countertops, large center island, pantry, stainless appliances and opens to the Great Room. Hardwood flooring throughout the downstairs. Master Suite with amazing walk-in closet; garden tub and separate shower. Spacious bedrooms with large closets. Conveniently located, minutes from McEntire, Fort Jackson, VA Hospital, 25 minutes from Shaw AFB. Huge Privacy fenced backyard with patio. Finished 2-car garage, endless hot water heater, central vacuum system and sprinkler system.
